        Selling Around Easter and Anzac Day in Brisbane
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Easter and Anzac Day cluster across late March to late April every year, and the resulting four-week stretch of long weekends and school holidays meaningfully changes how a Brisbane sale campaign should be timed and run. Here is the strategic playbook for sellers.
      </p>
